# Group Retail Trading

## POST /retail/quote
This endpoint allows quote the price of currency pair

##### Request Definition

| Fields        | Description   | Example 
| ------------- |---------------|---------
| nonce    | Ever increasing integer |
| quoteRequest | see Quote Request |


##### Quote Request

| Fields        | Description   | Example 
| ------------- |---------------|---------
|tradedCurrency | traded currency
|settlementCurrency | settlement currency
|tradedCurrencyAmount | traded currency amount
|settlementCurrencyAmount | settlement currency amount
|buyTradedCurrency | true for buy currency | false for sell
|isIndicativeQuote | for for retail quote
|customRef | customer reference in uuid format


##### Response Definition

| Fields        | Description   | Example
| ------------- |---------------|---------
|resultCode | result Code
|timestamp | unix timestamp | 
|quoteResponse | see Quote Response


##### Quote Response

| Fields        | Description   | Example
| ------------- |---------------|---------
| responseCode | see QuoteResponseCode
| buyTradedCurrency | true for buy  or false for sell
| tradedCurrency| tradedCurrency currency | e.g. BTC
| settlementCurrency | settlement currency | e.g. USD
| quotedSettlementCurrencyAmount | quoted settlement currency amount
| quotedTradedCurrencyAmount | quoted traded currency amount
|quotedAmountToDeliver | quoted amount to deliver
|wholesaleRateInSettlementCurrency | wholesale rate in settlement currency
|retailRateInSettlementCurrency | retail rate in settlement currency
|customRef | custom refernece 
|quoteId | quote id
|quoteExpiresAt | timestamp which the quote is expired at
|quoteCreatedAt | timestamp which the quote is created at
|maxAmount | max amount

+ Response 200(application/json)

    + Body
    
            {
               "resultCode": "OK",
               "exists": true
            }
            
            
## POST /retail/trade
This endpoint to trade order previously quote

##### Request Definition

| Fields        | Description   | Example 
| ------------- |---------------|---------
| nonce    | Ever increasing integer |
| tradeRequest | see Trade Request |


##### Trade Request

| Fields        | Description   | Example 
| ------------- |---------------|---------
| quoteId | quote Id 
| customRef | custom refernece  
| amount | amount in traded currency


##### Response Definition

| Fields        | Description   | Example
| ------------- |---------------|---------
|resultCode | result Code
| timestamp | unix timestamp | 
|tradeResponse | see Trade Response


##### Trade Response

| Fields        | Description   | Example
| ------------- |---------------|---------
| responseCode | see Trade Response Code
| tradeId | trade id
| quoteId| quote Id

##### Trade Response Code

| Fields        | Description   | 
| ------------- |---------------|
| INVALID_QUOTE_ID
| QUOTE_EXPIRED
| EXECUTED
| INSUFFICIENT_FUND
| ENGINE_NOT_AVAILABLE
| INSUFFICIENT_LIQUIDITY
| DISCOUNT_CODE_NOT_VALID,DAILY_LIMIT_EXCEEDED
| PENDING_EXECUTE
| MERCHANT_NOT_AVAILABLE

+ Response 200(application/json)

    + Body
    
            {
               "resultCode": "OK",
               "exists": true
            }
            
            
# Group Streaming

Streaming is based on socket.io, and does not support pure websockets (it is long polling).
Java or other language socket.io clients may work if they support long polling.

## Public Events

## Market Tick Event /public/tick/{market}/{ccyPair}
Get market ticks for a specific market and currency pair

### Subscription

| Fields        | Description| Example
| ------------- |-------------|---------
| market         | exchange market | BCT
| ccyPair        | currency pair |  BTCUSD (or any other supported currency pair, BTC as traded currency, USD as settlement currency)

### Event Definition

| Fields        | Description|  Example
| ------------- |-------------| ---------
| event       | event type | marketTick
| data       | see Market Tick | 


### Market Tick

| Fields        | Description|  Example
| ------------- |-------------| ---------
| market   | exchange market | BCT
| timestampMillis   | unix timestamp in millisecond | 1399711469626 in below example, which is equivalent to Sat, 10 May 2014 08:44:29 GMT
| bid   | best bid price | 551.16362 USD/BTC in below example
| ask   | best ask price| 584.28841 USD/BTC in below example
| volume   | traded volume in settlement currency in the past 24 hours | 2.25661368 USD
| vwap   | volume weighted average price of trades in the  past 24 hours | 567.88653298 USD/BTC
| high   | highest price of trades in the past 24 hours | 580.519619 USD/BTC
| low   | lowest price of trades in the past 24 hours | 554.718747 USD/BTC
| ccyPair   | currency pair | BTCUSD 
| last   | price of latest trade as of data.timestampMillis | 554.718747 USD/BTC



### Example JSON 

```javascript
    {
      "event": "marketTick",
      "data": [
        {
          "market": "BCT",
          "timestampMillis": 1399711469626,
          "bid": 551.16362,
          "ask": 584.28841,
          "volume": 2.25661368,
          "vwap": 567.88653298,
          "high": 580.519619,
          "low": 554.718747,
          "ccyPair": "BTCUSD",
          "last": 554.718747
        }
      ]
    }
```

## Order Book Update   public/orderBook/{market}/{ccyPair}
Get order book for a specific market and currency pair

### Subscription

| Fields        | Description| Example
| ------------- |-------------|---------
| market         | BCT |
| ccyPair        | currency pair | BTCUSD (or any other supported currency pair, BTC as traded currency, USD as settlement currency)

### Event Definition

| Fields        | Description|  Example
| ------------- |-------------| ---------
| event       | event type | orderBook
| data | order book

### Order Book
| Fields        | Description|  Example
| ------------- |-------------| ---------
| market   |  BCT | BCT
| ccyPair   | currency pair | BTCUSD 
| timestampMillis   | unix timestamp in millisecond | 1399713934547
| bids | all bid orders. See Order |
| asks | all ask orders. See Order |

### Order

| Fields        | Description|  Example
| ------------- |-------------| ---------
| price   | price of  orders; best order(s) (with highest price) is(/are) on top of the book | 551.16362 USD/BTC 
| quantity   | aggregated quantity of orders at the specific price | 1.48308644 BTC 
| total   | price*(aggregated )quantity of orders at the specific price | 817.42 USD

